collectionMetadata.name: National Library Singapore Archived Websites
collectionMetadata.description:
This dataset is a list of Singapore websites archived by the National Library, Singapore.  

These materials are a valuable resource for researchers to study websites which may no longer exist or observe changes in specific websites over time. Together, these websites reflect various aspects of Singaporean life, culture, and history in the 21st century.

For enquiries, please email ref@nlb.gov.sg

datasetMetadata.name: National Library Singapore Archived Websites 2024
datasetMetadata.description:
This dataset is a list of Singapore websites archived by the National Library, Singapore. It includes websites that can be accessed remotely online as well as those which can only be accessed onsite at Lee Kong Chian Reference Library, Level 11. 

These materials are a valuable resource for researchers to study websites which may no longer exist or observe changes in specific websites over time. Together, these websites reflect various aspects of Singaporean life, culture, and history in the 21st century.

For enquiries, please email ref@nlb.gov.sg
